---

## File structure explained

```
api/claude.js    — Sends AI analysis requests to Anthropic (keeps your key secret)
api/quote.js     — Fetches stock prices from Yahoo Finance (no CORS issues)
api/finnhub.js   — Fetches news + fundamentals from Finnhub (keeps your key secret)
public/index.html — The entire frontend app (HTML + CSS + JS in one file)
vercel.json      — Tells Vercel how to route requests
```

---

## Troubleshooting

**Stocks not loading?**
- Check Vercel → Functions → look for errors in `api/quote.js`

**No news showing?**
- Make sure `FINNHUB_API_KEY` is set in Vercel Environment Variables
- Redeploy after adding keys

**AI analysis not working?**
- Make sure `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` is set in Vercel Environment Variables
- Check you have credit at console.anthropic.com

**Seeing old data?**
- Hard refresh: Cmd+Shift+R (Mac) or Ctrl+Shift+R (Windows)
